import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom'

import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'
import './Navbar.css' 


export default class extends Component {

    render() {
  
        return (
            <Navbar collapseOnSelect expand="lg" className="bg-custom-2" style={{paddingBottom: "10px", marginTop: "20px"}}>
              <Navbar.Brand href='#' ><Link to="/"><Navbar className="title">PORTFOLIO </Navbar></Link></Navbar.Brand>  
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="basic-navbar-nav" />
                <Navbar.Collapse id="basic-navbar-nav">
                    <Nav className="ml-auto"  >
                        <Nav.Link></Nav.Link><Link className="links" to="/">Inicio</Link>
                        <Link className="links" to="/resume">Resume</Link>
                        <Link className="links" to="/projects">Projects</Link>
                        <Link className="links" to="/">Contacto</Link>
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Navbar>
        )
    }
}
